data.description: Located in the heart of one of Rosamond's most desirable westside communities, this single story family home is nestled near the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, and ready for your moving truck to unload. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home boasts a beautifully upgraded kitchen with granite counters, custom cabinetry and gorgeous stainless appliances. Just off of the kitchen is a bonus area that currently serves as an additional breakfast / coffee bar area and also an office / reading room. It's a perfect office option if all of the bedrooms are needed as bedrooms. Both bathrooms boast beautiful upgraded vanities with quartz counters, and the master bath also has an incredibly spacious, updated shower. The common areas feature gorgeous wood looking tile flooring and the bedrooms have newer carpet. Fully surrounded by extra tall privacy fencing, the backyard is ready for your parties with a covered patio, fire pit lounge area, plumbed in bbq, and sizable shed for extra storage. The home features a fairly new security system that is owned outright and comes with the property. You'll have both an evaporative cooler that chills the house beautifully on a dime, and also an A/C unit for those extra humid days. Located only 20 minutes from both Edwards Air Force Base and 20 minutes from Lancaster, this home is perfectly located to make your commute an easier one. With biking & hiking trails just around the corner in addition to some great schools and shopping options...this home is a perfect choice! Don't hesitate as this one won't last long!
